snippet.title: DOOM II  - New Wad - Austrian Avian Association - Sampler, Map 02 Sidhlwinkl Circus - UV - First Try
snippet.description:
So....ever think total conversions compatible in limit-removing ports are rare these days? Well, Mundy C has you covered! Taking place in a unique fantasy setting with an ortho protagonist, it's definitely nothing like Doom in anything but the gameplay sense. The Dehacked takes some getting used to but the detailing is just absolutely wonderful, the only concern in this map perhaps being a scarcity of ammo. Definitely something to look in to!


Played in From Doom with Love
Get it here
https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/135951-austrian-avian-association-aaa-eight-levels-of-1800s-fun/
